    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It\u2019s been garage-kept, smells like new, and drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is; it's basically like buying brand new. Perfect for someone who wants that 'fresh off the lot' feel! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will love it as much as I have!",
