    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, finished in flawless Arctic Silver Metallic over black full-leather. This 996.2 variant features the venerable 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, producing 315 hp and 273 lb-ft of torque. Mechanically beyond reproach, the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with an LN Engineering solution, alongside a fresh rear main seal (RMS). The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp, short-throw engagement, delivering power to an advanced all-wheel-drive system with a viscous coupling. The chassis benefits from the C4S-standard Turbo-spec suspension and braking systems, including four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors. Every component, from the Variocam Plus timing to the factory-optioned sport exhaust, functions with factory precision. This is a collector-quality specimen with a documented service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Mint condition. Single owner. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Garage kept. Full service history included.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
