    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, showcasing its original, deep-gloss factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather still retains its factory scent and supple texture, while the carpets have been protected by original mats since day one. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the mechanical performance is crisp, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. Accompanied by a full, documented service history, original window sticker, and both sets of keys, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to own a truly pristine, investment-grade example.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in an immaculate state, reflecting meticulous stewardship and an uncompromising commitment to preservation. Its condition is virtually indistinguishable from its original delivery state, offering the discerning enthusiast an unparalleled acquisition opportunity. We invite you to secure this benchmark example.",
