    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s an absolute dream! It\u2019s been babied since day one, garage-kept, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is absolutely spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
