    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 era. This unit features a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission paired with a GKN variable M-differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The S65 powerplant, derived from the S85 V10, utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. This vehicle is mechanically impeccable, with preventative rod bearing replacement already performed using VAC-treated shells and ARP hardware. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing exceptional lateral stability and damping frequency adjustment. The factory Alpine White finish is flawless, and the subframe mounting points show zero stress fatigue. A purist\u2019s specification in showroom condition, maintained with zero regard for cost.",
